CONTRAINDICATIONS

Carteolol is contraindicated in those individuals with bronchial asthma or with a history of bronchial asthma, or severe chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (see 
WARNINGS
); sinus bradycardia; second- and third-degree atrioventricular block; overt cardiac failure (see 
WARNINGS
); cardiogenic shock; or hypersensivity to any component of this product.
